header.gameNote: NCAA Women's Championship pres. by Capital One - Final Four

videos.description: South Carolina's Aliyah Boston explains her emotions after defeating Louisville to advance to the women's national championship game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Interview (Aliyah Boston: 'We're not going home') 2022/04/01

videos.headline: Aliyah Boston: 'We're not going home'

videos.description: With heartbreak still present from the 2021 Final Four loss, Aliyah Boston explains how South Carolina dug deep and earned a championship bid.
videos.headline: Boston proud of Gamecocks for making it 'over the hump'

videos.description: South Carolina turns back Louisville, 72-59, in a Final Four semifinal battle between 1-seeds to earn the chance at another national championship.
videos.headline: Gamecocks beat Louisville, will play for NCAA title

videos.description: SEC Now analysts Steffi Sorenson and Alyssa Lang break down the key difference-makers for South Carolina to beat Louisville in the Final Four.
videos.headline: Defense, great shooting were key in Gamecocks' win
